            <!---========= Start Features Of Learning Management System (LMS)===============-->
            <section class="my-5 features__of__lms" id="Features">
                <div class="container pb-3">
                    <h2 class="h2__heading2 text-center animate__fadeInDown wow animated"><span>Features Of</span><br />
                        Learning Management System (LMS)</h2>
                    <p class="text-center mb-3">
                        An LMS comes equipped with a range of features that enable organizations to create, deliver,
                            <br />
                        and manage their training programs effectively.
                    </p>

                    <div class="row ">
                        <div class="col-lg-3 col-md-6 mt-5">
                            <div class="bg-white p-3 mb-3 rounded shadow text-center  feature-box h-100">
                                <img loading="lazy" src="img/Course-Creation.webp" class="img-fluid" alt="LMS-banner" width="102" height="100">
                                <h3 class="fw-bold mt-3">Course Creation</h3>
                                <p>Enable institutions to create and manage their training content, which includes assessments, course materials, and learning activities. </p>
                            </div>
                        </div>
                        <div class="col-lg-3 col-md-6 mt-5">
                            <div class="bg-white p-3 mb-3 rounded shadow text-center  feature-box h-100">
                                <img loading="lazy" src="img/Content-Delivery.webp" class="img-fluid" alt="LMS-banner" width="102" height="100">
                                <h3 class="fw-bold mt-3">Content Delivery</h3>
                                <p>Allow schools and colleges to deliver their training material to students in multimedia formats, including videos, PDFs, PPTs, documents, interactive simulations, etc.</p>
                            </div>
                        </div>
                        <div class="col-lg-3 col-md-6 mt-5">
                            <div class="bg-white p-3 mb-3 rounded shadow text-center  feature-box h-100">
                                <img loading="lazy" src="img/User-Management.webp" class="img-fluid" alt="LMS-banner" width="102" height="100">
                                <h3 class="fw-bold mt-3">User Management</h3>
                                <p>An LMS enables institutes to effectively manage their students, such as adding new users, providing login credentials, creating user groups, and assigning permissions.</p>
                            </div>
                        </div>
                        <div class="col-lg-3 col-md-6 mt-5">
                            <div class="bg-white p-3 mb-3 rounded shadow text-center  feature-box h-100">
