                                <h3 class="fw-bold mt-3">Analytics & Reporting</h3>
                                <p>Administrators can easily track their training program’s effectiveness via deep analytics and BI reporting tools and offer insights about student's performance, course completion rate, etc.</p>
                            </div>
                        </div>
                        <div class="col-lg-3 col-md-6 mt-5">
                            <div class="bg-white p-3 mb-3 rounded shadow text-center  feature-box h-100">
