                                <h3 class="fw-bold mt-3">Certification and Compliance Management</h3>
                                <p>Help institutions to monitor and manage their certifications, compliance training programs, and licenses. Set reminders to stay updated on any changes.</p>
                            </div>
                        </div>
                        <div class="col-lg-3 col-md-6 mt-5">
                            <div class="bg-white p-3 mb-3 rounded shadow text-center  feature-box h-100">
                                <img loading="lazy" src="img/Gamification.webp" class="img-fluid" alt="LMS-banner" width="102" height="100">
                                <h3 class="fw-bold mt-3">Gamification of Courses</h3>
                                <p>Offers advanced gamification capabilities that makes learning more interactive and engaging by including game-like features such as badges, points, and leaderboards.</p>
