                                        <div class="content col-sm-11">
                                            <p class="text-white mb-3 wow animate__animated animate__fadeInDown">An LMS is similar to a virtual classroom, providing a collaborative online space for learners and instructors to engage in interactive learning experiences. It has a vast repository of educational resources in easy-to-understand and multimedia formats.</p>
                                            <p class="text-white mb-3 wow animate__animated animate__fadeInDown">The institutions are required to create user accounts for students, administrators, and teachers. After setting up different accounts and providing role-based login access, the faculty can create and upload courses, while students can access these content and track their progress regularly over time.</p>
