                                <div class="accordion" id="myAccordion">
                                    <div class="accordion-item mb-3">
                                        <h5 class="accordion-header" id="headingOne">
                                            <button type="button" class="accordion-button" data-bs-toggle="collapse" data-bs-target="#collapseOne">1. Who Needs an LMS Software?</button>
                                        </h5>
                                        <div id="collapseOne" class="accordion-collapse show" data-bs-parent="#myAccordion">
                                            <div class="card-body p-3">
                                                <p>An LMS can be helpful for educational institutions such as K-12 schools, colleges, and universities, as well as for businesses who offer employee training & development programs. Also, independent trainers who want to create and sell their own online courses can also benefit from using an LMS software.</p>
                                            </div>
                                        </div>
                                    </div>
                                    <div class="accordion-item mb-3">
                                        <h5 class="accordion-header" id="headingTwo">
                                            <button type="button" class="accordion-button  collapsed" data-bs-toggle="collapse" data-bs-target="#collapseTwo">2. Why Use a Learning Management System?</button>
                                        </h5>
                                        <div id="collapseTwo" class="accordion-collapse collapse " data-bs-parent="#myAccordion">
                                            <div class="card-body  p-3">
                                                <p>By using an LMS , educational institutions can reduce costs associated with traditional classroom-based training, improve the efficiency of the teaching programs, and provide learners with a more interactive learning experience. Moreover, it allows for better tracking of learner progress and performance, which can help institutions make data-driven decisions to improve their teaching programs.</p>
                                            </div>
                                        </div>
                                    </div>
                                    <div class="accordion-item mb-3">
                                        <h5 class="accordion-header" id="headingThree">
                                            <button type="button" class="accordion-button collapsed" data-bs-toggle="collapse" data-bs-target="#collapseThree">3. What are the Advantages of an LMS ?</button>
                                        </h5>
                                        <div id="collapseThree" class="accordion-collapse collapse" data-bs-parent="#myAccordion">
                                            <div class="card-body  p-3">
                                                <ul>
                                                    <li>Increases accessibility of course content anytime, anywhere, and on any device </li>
                                                    <li>Enhances learning engagement and retention through multimedia elements</li>
                                                    <li>Facilitates collaboration and communication among learners and teachers </li>
                                                    <li>Provides real-time tracking and reporting of learner progress, performance, and feedback </li>
                                                    <li>Enables customization and personalization of learning paths to meet individual student needs and preferences.</li>

                                                </ul>
                                            </div>
                                        </div>
                                    </div>

